<item>
            <title>[LU-429] Debug message cleanup in filter_connect()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-429</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The message in filter_connect() incorrectly says &quot;Received MDS connection&quot;.  This function appears to be used by both the mdt and ost code now, so it shouldn&apos;t say &quot;MDS&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We really don&apos;t want to see this message on the console either, so I moved it to D_INFO.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
